  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/5807b9b437568f35894fd4d4fcf62168.avif?t=1736824332\" width=616 height=79 /></span><br><br><strong>DADOO: Twists, Turns, and Mischiefs is a Snake and Ladder Game, with superpowers!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/943c1faaf6790a189f7815e9e08389cc.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/943c1faaf6790a189f7815e9e08389cc.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/943c1faaf6790a189f7815e9e08389cc.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to the mad, chaotic, and thrilling world of DADOO - a reinvention of the classic Snake and Ladder game that you thought you knew so well! <br><br>This is no ordinary multiplayer game. It's a ruthless battlefield where your strategic thinking will be tested. Do not rely on luck, and the only thing that you can trust is yourself. But remember, there's more to this game than simply reaching the top. Enjoy the ride, let the chaos unfold, and don't forget to make the others feel miserable.<br><br>So, what are you waiting for? Roll the dice, play your cards, and invite your friend into the pandemonium of chaos. Just make sure you're still friends after playing <strong>DADOO: Twists, Turns, and Mischiefs</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/35c8173428f9e268468c26e71157061e.avif?t=1736824332\" width=616 height=79 /></span><br><br><strong>1. There are Snakes.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/bd3e4849f4f1b9a14e4031e4a0b14769.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/bd3e4849f4f1b9a14e4031e4a0b14769.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/bd3e4849f4f1b9a14e4031e4a0b14769.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2. There are ladders (They are cannons in this gif, tho). </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/b71dcacfad4205a1c9c38ede4c7d8b69.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/b71dcacfad4205a1c9c38ede4c7d8b69.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/b71dcacfad4205a1c9c38ede4c7d8b69.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3. More than 20 superpower cards that you can use to attack your enemy (Or defend too!)</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/51f99587c10cfa2f4fc9dfb7e61443d3.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/51f99587c10cfa2f4fc9dfb7e61443d3.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/51f99587c10cfa2f4fc9dfb7e61443d3.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4. Cross-platform multiplayer game! Play the game together with your friend on the PC and Android smartphones.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/a3f7c0f4c273bd3ec5a8795050ad342c.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/a3f7c0f4c273bd3ec5a8795050ad342c.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/a3f7c0f4c273bd3ec5a8795050ad342c.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>5. Multiple languages support, including English, Indonesian, Portuguese, Korean, and Japanese.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/ab997f2bd8869be4a999a348c4a453d0.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/ab997f2bd8869be4a999a348c4a453d0.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/ab997f2bd8869be4a999a348c4a453d0.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>6. Various cute mascot characters to choose from.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/8ea3e5ad5235806144aa901c1729dbd1.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/8ea3e5ad5235806144aa901c1729dbd1.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/8ea3e5ad5235806144aa901c1729dbd1.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>7. Oh, each character has their own unique superpower too.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/2184721b659da4044258c7fe8c3f139b.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/2184721b659da4044258c7fe8c3f139b.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/2184721b659da4044258c7fe8c3f139b.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Buy the Steam version of Dadoo and get an exclusive bundle! Unlock a new card and skin with this unique offer.</strong>",
